<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Homenagem à Virgem Maria</title>
  <!-- Fonte elegante -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fdf6f0, #c9d7e0);
      color: #2c3e50;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .marian-box {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 650px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .marian-box:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .quote {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #34495e;
    }

    button {
      background-color: #2980b9;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #1c5980;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .halo {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 4px solid rgba(255, 223, 0, 0.7);
      position: absolute;
      top: -50px;
      left: calc(50% - 75px);
      animation: rotate 6s linear infinite;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 223, 0, 0.5);
    }

    @keyframes rotate {
      0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>Homenagem à Virgem Maria</h1>

  <div class="marian-box">
    <div class="halo"></div>
    <div class="quote" id="quote">
      “Ave Maria, cheia de graça, o Senhor é contigo.”
    </div>
    <button id="newQuoteBtn">Nova Mensagem</button>
  </div>

  <footer>Inspirado na fé e devoção à Virgem Maria</footer>

 <script src="/main.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
